arrayOfProducts.name: Are we there yet?
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Looking for a Free Bedtime story books? Jim and Jen are going to the zoo and the drive never seems to end. EVER! They just made a song for the road and the tune is growing on mom and dad.Let’s tap our feet and sing along..

arrayOfProducts.name: I found a frog
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Something magical was happening in the fish bowl  and he wasn’t  quite ready for what lay in store.  Read this captivating free illustrated book for kids that encourages them to explore and be awed by the many wonders of nature.

arrayOfProducts.name: A dog on a log
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Is there ever an ordinary day at the beach? Read what happens when a flea, a dog and a hog meet on a warm sunny day by the sea.  This Free Children’s Book is great read for children aged 3 to 8.

arrayOfProducts.name: Do you wounder about rain snow
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: “What’s to wonder about water?”, you might ask. Professor Ture will tell you why.  Filled with compelling illustrations, this free children’s book takes a dive  into a whirlpool of knowledge about the ubiquitous water that we often take for granted.

arrayOfProducts.name: Dragons
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Dragons come in many shapes and sizes and speak different tongues. Some are mean, some are kind, some have legs while some don’t. No matter what they all have one thing in common..they grab eyes wherever they go.  Join our free children’s book giveaway to read more about these wonderful creatures.

arrayOfProducts.name: The hike
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Mandy and grandpa went on a hike . But it was more than that. Together they explored the woods, learnt to be at peace with nature and talked their hearts out about things that mattered. It was a special bond between them and you’ve got to read this great free illustrated children’s book to experience it. Happy Exploring!!

arrayOfProducts.name: The pirates cove
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Sandy chances upon an old treasure map and as the events roll out one after another, he becomes richer both by pennies and by thoughts. Here’s a treasure hunt to embark upon  in this free children’s storybook. Sail Away Captain! The seven seas are yours.

arrayOfProducts.name: The way of the woods
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: Shh!  Did you hear that? The jungle’s saying a story and you cannot afford to miss it. A colorful narrative set in the woods..camouflaged as a free children’s dog story. Happy Reading!

arrayOfProducts.name: Bully Bill
arrayOfProducts.author: Bilkis Ismail
arrayOfProducts.details: He thought he was the Lord of the Farm. He thought he was Boss. But his vanity was short lived and soon he learnt a lesson he’ll never forget. Follow this funny and thoughtful story of a certain farm we chanced upon in this free bedtime storybook.
